{"id": "ChIJ8x15VLvbwoARKvNhy2Xi3LY", "rating": 4.6, "userRatingCount": 229, "displayName": {"text": "UG Tea -San Gabriel", "languageCode": "en"}, "reviews": [{"name": "places/ChIJ8x15VLvbwoARKvNhy2Xi3LY/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2kxQ2JuWlJaRVJNUkZKS05YYzFUM00wTTNkNU4wRRAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "2 months ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "Visited this newly opened boba spot and was really impressed by the space. It’s large with multiple areas for aesthetics photos.\n\nTried the Cloud Matcha Latte. It was creamy and smooth. Overall, a great spot to hang out, take photos, and enjoy a solid drink. Would come back.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "Visited this newly opened boba spot and was really impressed by the space. It’s large with multiple areas for aesthetics photos.\n\nTried the Cloud Matcha Latte. It was creamy and smooth. Overall, a great spot to hang out, take photos, and enjoy a solid drink. Would come back.", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Natcha Muangsomboon", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/113052457072323064457/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWHOXUI8oUISHE13wZqgV1Agk0rEl_k0vlze7-Xlp8exb6Qk4lr=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba4"}, "publishTime": "2026-04-30T16:34:17.504078512Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2kxQ2JuWlJaRVJNUkZKS05YYzFUM00wTTNkNU4wRRAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2kxQ2JuWlJaRVJNUkZKS05YYzFUM00wTTNkNU4wRRAB!2m1!1s0x80c2dbbb54791df3:0xb6dce265cb61f32a"}, {"name": "places/ChIJ8x15VLvbwoARKvNhy2Xi3LY/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2taNVZFMVBRbmRtWmtNeWJWbFhObGxsYlhWSWNVRRAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "a month ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "Tried the new avocado mango smoothie at UG\ntoday and it was actually sooo good\nDidn't think avocado + mango would work together, but it's super creamy, fruity, and refreshing without being too heavy or sweet.\nAlso got the limited plushie for +$2.99 and now I fully understand why everyone's collecting them\nThe exclusive bag is cute too.\nTheir matcha drinks are really solid too -- strong matcha flavor but still smooth and not bitter.\nCute interior, photo booth inside, and overall such a fun spot to hang out for a bit.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "Tried the new avocado mango smoothie at UG\ntoday and it was actually sooo good\nDidn't think avocado + mango would work together, but it's super creamy, fruity, and refreshing without being too heavy or sweet.\nAlso got the limited plushie for +$2.99 and now I fully understand why everyone's collecting them\nThe exclusive bag is cute too.\nTheir matcha drinks are really solid too -- strong matcha flavor but still smooth and not bitter.\nCute interior, photo booth inside, and overall such a fun spot to hang out for a bit.", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Jessie", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/115146699069447234273/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocL5wNuQCWLGTBOSott40kfXWs-8XiX1g3uiCWpoZOz2PBiOTw=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba4"}, "publishTime": "2026-05-21T16:23:19.216149554Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2taNVZFMVBRbmRtWmtNeWJWbFhObGxsYlhWSWNVRRAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2taNVZFMVBRbmRtWmtNeWJWbFhObGxsYlhWSWNVRRAB!2m1!1s0x80c2dbbb54791df3:0xb6dce265cb61f32a"}, {"name": "places/ChIJ8x15VLvbwoARKvNhy2Xi3LY/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2xSaWVEVnZiQzFrZFU1TGFEbHFlR2xUUVRsb00xRRAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "5 months ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "Very interesting concept for this tea place! Everything is white and grass green (kind of nature-y), and the decorations are a throwback. But the real highlight is the teas! The aroma, fragrance, and flavor of the camellia teas really came through even though floral teas are more subtle. I also got a rice tea with floral jelly and the jelly was chewy and actually tasted floral. They really make their teas well here.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "Very interesting concept for this tea place! Everything is white and grass green (kind of nature-y), and the decorations are a throwback. But the real highlight is the teas! The aroma, fragrance, and flavor of the camellia teas really came through even though floral teas are more subtle. I also got a rice tea with floral jelly and the jelly was chewy and actually tasted floral. They really make their teas well here.", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Amy Y", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/106296843800541593082/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLCHz6QMVZkDrDJw6k_zpjXMdiw-4Ctlo-DncbK-WSJ0NNcBlnW=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba5"}, "publishTime": "2026-02-06T01:16:32.963523079Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2xSaWVEVnZiQzFrZFU1TGFEbHFlR2xUUVRsb00xRRAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2xSaWVEVnZiQzFrZFU1TGFEbHFlR2xUUVRsb00xRRAB!2m1!1s0x80c2dbbb54791df3:0xb6dce265cb61f32a"}, {"name": "places/ChIJ8x15VLvbwoARKvNhy2Xi3LY/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2xaQmR6UTROMnRLZUdKcE1HazFWemRsZGs1T05sRRAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "a month ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "Really like this tea house. Got the light milk tea with jasmine (三窨十五茉-轻乳茶), tea aroma is clean and soft, the UG-style milk feels smooth but not heavy, so it tastes kind of guilt-free for me. Also tried a matcha latte, pretty rich with a gentle sweet finish that lingers a bit. Space inside is bright and roomy, lots of light, nice for photos and just sitting with friends, tbh I kind of lost track of time. Staff felt easygoing and patient with my order.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "Really like this tea house. Got the light milk tea with jasmine (三窨十五茉-轻乳茶), tea aroma is clean and soft, the UG-style milk feels smooth but not heavy, so it tastes kind of guilt-free for me. Also tried a matcha latte, pretty rich with a gentle sweet finish that lingers a bit. Space inside is bright and roomy, lots of light, nice for photos and just sitting with friends, tbh I kind of lost track of time. Staff felt easygoing and patient with my order.", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Joyce Tsai", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/105652152120247846836/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJlLM76M7qU0XtwRuhhMY4UaIsFwojIZLd6IEhUgTacV2g6ZQ=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba4"}, "publishTime": "2026-06-14T02:18:42.581311197Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2xaQmR6UTROMnRLZUdKcE1HazFWemRsZGs1T05sRRAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2xaQmR6UTROMnRLZUdKcE1HazFWemRsZGs1T05sRRAB!2m1!1s0x80c2dbbb54791df3:0xb6dce265cb61f32a"}, {"name": "places/ChIJ8x15VLvbwoARKvNhy2Xi3LY/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2pCWGQzZHlSWGhvUkdGR1dYRlZSVGRJZWxFeGNtYxAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "4 months ago", "rating": 4, "text": {"text": "This place is super viral and popular. So let’s see if they’re pretty good eh or ew. Vibes were on point and I got their rice floral green milk tea with creamy oat and matcha cookie smoothie at whatever the server’s recommended sweetness was to try. The milk tea was milky, not sweet, had light tea flaves, and plenty of chewy yummy oats at the bottom. The matcha cookie smoothie was topped with a lightly sweet whipped cream and biscoff cookie, was pretty icy like a slush, not sweet, had light matchay flaves with a bit of biscoff crumbs sprinkled throughout. My bad for not asking for the drinks sweeter like I like them cuz overall these were eh.\n\nRice floral green milk tea L $6.75\nCreamy oat $0.75\nMatcha cookie smoothie $6.95", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "This place is super viral and popular. So let’s see if they’re pretty good eh or ew. Vibes were on point and I got their rice floral green milk tea with creamy oat and matcha cookie smoothie at whatever the server’s recommended sweetness was to try. The milk tea was milky, not sweet, had light tea flaves, and plenty of chewy yummy oats at the bottom. The matcha cookie smoothie was topped with a lightly sweet whipped cream and biscoff cookie, was pretty icy like a slush, not sweet, had light matchay flaves with a bit of biscoff crumbs sprinkled throughout. My bad for not asking for the drinks sweeter like I like them cuz overall these were eh.\n\nRice floral green milk tea L $6.75\nCreamy oat $0.75\nMatcha cookie smoothie $6.95", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "AC9", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/114415861027882176583/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWiFfpOc9nsCcCI97_K0ntJYjx5NEVbNmjYETYfc21YuGhkhUgC=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba6"}, "publishTime": "2026-02-24T01:48:32.289221071Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2pCWGQzZHlSWGhvUkdGR1dYRlZSVGRJZWxFeGNtYxAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2pCWGQzZHlSWGhvUkdGR1dYRlZSVGRJZWxFeGNtYxAB!2m1!1s0x80c2dbbb54791df3:0xb6dce265cb61f32a"}], "photos": [{"name": "places/ChIJ8x15VLvbwoARKvNhy2Xi3LY/photos/AWCwydidQXAkfh4B82GK8rS-PH4n0MXFHFbRQSGTb0iv8xaZgUmo848InGK9eVyPwqxsnXDLIn-8kf70xiI52qJi8EEUfBkRU2d2ZFQar76VVabbpYypd8paBAbQadAwP6EQa32joxSRyMOPZjvC738vjGsbftPM-_KxMuoh6MUukgOTMluCe4FurUl6qCZqFVn